item.description:
Queries A collection of queries for inspecting data stored in a Prometheus server. Most of these queries should work in vanilla prometheus however a small number may contain a few &ldquo;grafana-isms&rdquo;
The following variables are used as examples
   Name Description     $interval A time interval e.g. 1m. 5m, 1h etc.    Nodes Queries relating to the state of the &ldquo;physical&rdquo; hardware that is hosting the cluster
